{"tid":57181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最少兩賊在逃　操普通話疑是偷渡客　埋伏多時等劫婦孺","createTime":"2016-12-27T20:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T13:36:30.000Z","uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f861008a215920888b6f9c19d9394b6e815245bc","tid":57181,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:08:06.000Z","msg":"巿民行山熱點的長沙灣鷹巢山今午發生連環劫案，兩批共5名巿民先後遇上刀匪，損失現金及手機等財物。現場消息稱，最少有兩名操普通話的匪徒犯案，事後逃去無蹤。警方懷疑匪徒是非法入境者，目前有大批機動部隊警員在山上搜捕。<br />\n<br />\n今日為公眾假期，據悉鷹巢山遊人眾多，警方懷疑賊人埋伏在山上暗處，等候單獨行山人士或老弱巿民才打劫。<br />\n<br />\n首宗劫案發生於中午約12時40分，一名六旬女子獨自行經鷹巢山自然教育徑時，突然被一名賊人用左手箍頸，右手持刀指嚇事主。賊人搶去女子數十元及一部手機後離開。<br />\n<br />\n約7分鐘後，有一家四口再於案發現場附近遇上刀匪，被搶走1000元現金、一條金鏈及兩部手機。一名男子抗賊時受輕傷，但拒絕送院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161227/s00001/1482829319373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161227%2Fs00001%2F1482829319373&d=NohmppOcrP8OYqKDbJf%2BYJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=b789ae97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161227%2Fs00001%2F1482829319373&h=30f9751a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161227/s00001/1482829319373</a>"},{"pid":"f5bc09f6bd5e1ba5cecb31f520f498a4619ef4ff","tid":57181,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T00:44:25.000Z","msg":"專材"},{"pid":"9074715861e1e21159d1332e09839e0709cb3dbd","tid":57181,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T00:53:05.000Z","msg":"自由行唔比呀"},{"pid":"80762d0dfeaac5a188803a7287aa2f88af1d6b9f","tid":57181,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:01:23.000Z","msg":"包容下啦香港人"},{"pid":"c2662b9add95ea6cbc306d4e02a2877f28934a06","tid":57181,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:02:59.000Z","msg":"諗住去行山避